WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.630 --> 00:00:11.990
Swipe down from the notifications bar, tap the "Settings" icon

00:00:11.990 --> 00:00:13.802
Tap the "General" tab

00:00:13.802 --> 00:00:17.872
Tap "Guest Mode"

00:00:17.872 --> 00:00:20.038
Tap the switch at top to enable/disable it

00:00:20.038 --> 00:00:23.681
Tap "OK" to confirm we are going to set pattern lock

00:00:23.681 --> 00:00:25.845
Tap "Pattern"

00:00:25.845 --> 00:00:28.895
Draw an unlock pattern for normal mode

00:00:28.895 --> 00:00:30.209
Tap "Continue"

00:00:30.209 --> 00:00:32.574
Draw it again to confirm

00:00:32.574 --> 00:00:34.212
Tap "Confirm"

00:00:34.212 --> 00:00:35.898
Tap "Yes"

00:00:35.898 --> 00:00:41.663
Enter a new backup PIN, use when you forget the pattern

00:00:41.663 --> 00:00:44.234
Tap "Set pattern"

00:00:44.234 --> 00:00:52.510
Draw an unlock pattern for Guest mode

00:00:52.510 --> 00:00:55.001
Tap "Set apps"

00:00:55.001 --> 00:00:56.478
Tap the "Add apps" icon at top

00:00:56.478 --> 00:01:01.821
Select the apps you can use in Guest mode and tap "OK"

00:01:01.821 --> 00:01:04.023
Back to the setting of Guest mode

00:01:04.023 --> 00:01:26.393
Demonstration

00:01:26.393 --> 00:01:43.883
You can only use the apps in Guest mode

